        </p>

        <h3>Disclaimer</h3>
        <p>
          This website is provided “as is” without warranties of any kind, either express or implied.
        </p>

        <h3>Limitation of liability</h3>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, we will not be liable for any damages arising out of or related to your use of this website.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
